{"tid":1834036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[準備再下一城]惠譽：持續多月示威和社會不滿　為香港評級帶來壓力","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T08:47:27.000Z","uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9be93a8e1ed6a3947e79395ebe7439c38313a809","tid":1834036,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>去年9月亦下調本港評級的惠譽，亞太區主權評級主管施帝文未有正面回應惠譽會否跟隨再度下調本港評級，不過提到持續多月的示威和社會不滿，令香港評級帶來壓力，目前正持續審視</strong>，但重申每次評級都會以經濟體未來1-2年的發展為基準，而政府龐大的財政儲備對香港的經濟前景有正面影響。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，近年香港在一國兩制下享有的經濟和政府管治的高度自主逐漸被侵蝕，中央對香港事務發聲的程度愈來愈高，去年下調香港評級，正反映一國兩制的指標正受挑戰，認為香港的評級前景面臨壓力。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽早前下調澳門評級，施帝文提醒，香港及澳門的信貸評級較內地高，主要是建基於一國兩制的差異，當兩地與中央的融合程度愈來愈高，港澳的評級將會反映差異進一步收窄的結果。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504182-20200122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504182-20200122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzX9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=866d7a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504182-20200122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1f25f0e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504182-20200122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c135afa708ff4a54a43aaa694f8dc683c71877dd","tid":1834036,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過山車"},{"pid":"74effab45d67c595c231bf41726a3610fbdfc9f6","tid":1834036,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bf9c1affc0fb49b71e1006805cbc5e7f552dd3","tid":1834036,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c135afa708ff4a54a43aaa694f8dc683c71877dd","tid":1834036,"uid":214502,"like":